'''施卢赫语'''（ⵜⴰⵛⵍⵃⵉⵜ ''Taclḥit''<ref>{{cite book|last=El Mountassir, Abdallah |url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/1141568167|title=Metodo di tachelhit : lingua amazigh (berbera) del Sud del Marocco : asselmd n-tchelhit|date=2017|publisher=Unior|others=Di Tolla, Anna Maria.|isbn=978-88-6719-148-2|location=Napoli|oclc=1141568167}}</ref>；{{lang-fr|Chleuh}}），又称'''希尔哈语'''（{{lang|ar|Šəlḥa}}；{{lang|en|Shilha}}<ref>When referring to the language, anthropologists and historians prefer the name "Shilha", which is in the Oxford English Dictionary (OED). Linguists writing in English prefer "Tashelhiyt".</ref>）、'''苏斯-柏柏尔语'''<ref name=Kossmann19>{{cite book|author=Maarten Kossmann|title=The Arabic Influence on Northern Berber|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Se-BAAAAQBAJ|year=2013|publisher=BRILL Academic|isbn=978-90-04-25309-4|pages=19–20|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122204341/https://books.google.com/books?id=Se-BAAAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author1=MG Kossmann|author2=HJ Stroomer|editor=Alan S Kaye|title=Phonologies of Asia and Africa: Including the Caucasus|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=T6jmziooEk0C|year=1997|publisher=Eisenbrauns|isbn=978-1-57506-019-4|pages=461–462|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211073628/https://books.google.com/books?id=T6jmziooEk0C|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一种[[柏柏尔语族|柏柏尔语言]]，[[施卢赫人|施卢赫人]]的母语，主要分布于[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]的[[小阿特拉斯山脉|小阿特拉斯山脉]]、[[高阿特拉斯山脉|高阿特拉斯山脉]]和[[苏斯河_(摩洛哥)|苏斯河谷]]地区。是[[阿加迪尔|阿加迪尔]]的传统语言。

施卢赫语有着富有特色的文学传统，存有许多16世纪晚期的手抄文献，以阿拉伯字母書寫。现代施卢赫语文学在20世纪70年代以来开始发展。2014年，有500万人使用施卢赫语，占摩洛哥人口的14.1%，是摩洛哥使用人数最多的柏柏尔语言<ref name="Comm">{{cite web|last1=Haut commissariat au Plan, Moroccan Kingdom|first1=Haut commissariat au Plan|title=Recensement général de la Maroc|url=http://rgphentableaux.hcp.ma/Default1/|website=HCP|publisher=Haut commissariat du Plan|accessdate=16 August 2016|language=fr|archive-date=2018-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181208035314/http://rgphentableaux.hcp.ma/Default1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。施卢赫语和一些柏柏尔语相比差别较大，如[[图阿雷格语|图阿雷格语]]<ref>Joseph R. Applegate (1957), [https://www.jstor.org/stable/4322927 Berber Studies I: Shilha] {{Wayback|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/4322927 |date=20210130063125 }}, Middle East Journal, Vol. 11, No. 3 (Summer, 1957), pages 324-327</ref>。

